This paper is primarily focused on object detection, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the use of deep learning methods and adversarial learning, which are common topics in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper deals with image quality and distribution alignment, which are relevant to multimedia (cs.MM) and robotics (cs.RO).
